{"tid":1344102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警，我屌你老母，你放元朗白兵走？有冇搞撚錯","createTime":"2019-07-21T20:31:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T23:06:00.000Z","uid":249616,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ca04fedef64c0a30c4d5404aba6ffff75f1f47d0","tid":1344102,"uid":249616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:31:08.000Z","msg":"有冇搞撚錯百幾個人你一個都唔拉，仲要當面放走晒<br />\n有冇搞撚錯。如果係你屋企人行過都畀人亂打，你班仆街黑警會點呀。睇到依家真係嬲到震！<br />\n警黑合作打人就合法冇罪，我地示威抗爭就係暴力罪行？<br />\n我從來冇諗過做勇武派，但係今日香港法治淪陷，政府警察聯合黑社會，唔單止襲擊示威者，仲襲擊一般市民，然後連掩飾都唔掩，公然展示暴力統治。<br />\n我唔想再和理非啦，再和理非只會助長暴政同黑警勢力<br />\n以暴易暴，唯一出路"},{"pid":"9719bc22d46d7cc09308b8f82772eae9d4fb6c0e","tid":1344102,"uid":190928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:31:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd19193a9e1ab283b9d19d039c256a920345a5ef","tid":1344102,"uid":38139,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:32:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣片</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/z-OPjVA7DEo \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fz-OPjVA7DEo%20&d=D9%2BIkncl4BF5lZ8wPV9kyBfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=0da165b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/z-OPjVA7DEo </a><br />\n<br />\n【石鏡泉】經濟日報執董<br />\n鼓吹元朗黑勢力&quot;打仔&quot;<br />\n<br />\n【何君堯】建制派議員<br />\n稱讚元朗暴徒喺英雄<br />\n<br />\n請share<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a528fcd800e52fdadc1482ec85730805462af75","tid":1344102,"uid":249616,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:39:39.000Z